{
  "text": "An evaluation of Wordvice AI, a proofreading tool, highlighted that the tool could outperform the built-in proofreading abilities of Google Docs or Microsoft Word, but still only managed to identify 77% of what was identified by a human proofreader (Heintz et al., 2022).",
